May is sent to the forests of Africa to try to stop some ruthless poachers. But the truth behind the massacre of innocent animals is very different, and Special Agent Alfa will need the help of a living legend ... Dawa Eghenghi!

Alexandra Sterling is a very popular television host. One night she is kidnapped, and then found alone along a road, her face completely disfigured. For her a new life starts that hides, however, a frightening secret that only Nathan Never can reveal ...

Many years ago Legs Weaver came into contact with an alien spacecraft, coming from the lost planet of Waldur. By means of the power of that equipment, Legs became Sonja, a legendary warrior. Now, the archive of stories told by Legs, managed by Kay, the adopted daughter of May Frayn, has a new adventure to tell

Nathan Never is able to find her, but their escape will be dramatic and reveal to each of the two have hidden sides of their personalities ...
